e=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td></tr><tr style=\";page-break-inside:avoid;height:30px\"><td width=\"51\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:25px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">18</span></p></td><td width=\"376\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">复习</span></p></td><td width=\"48\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:25px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">2</span></p></td><td width=\"48\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td></tr><tr style=\";page-break-inside:avoid;height:30px\"><td width=\"51\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:25px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">19</span></p></td><td width=\"376\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">复习</span></p></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td></tr><tr style=\";page-break-inside:avoid;height:30px\"><td width=\"51\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:25px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">20</span></p></td><td width=\"376\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">考试</span></p></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td></tr><tr style=\";page-break-inside:avoid;height:30px\"><td width=\"427\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">合</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">计</span></p></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:25px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\">70</span></p></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td><td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"30\"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"line-height:25px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">填表人（签字）：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\";font-family:宋体\">教研室主任（签字）：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\";font-family:宋体\">系部主任（签字）：</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;line-height:16px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;line-height:16px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">说明：</span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">、本表是教师授课的依据和学生课程学习的参考计划，请教师认真填写，打印一式二份（请使用</span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">A4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">纸正反打印），交系部存档。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36px;line-height:16px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">、按照教学大纲编排授课计划时应按照校历将法定假日编排进去，以保证达到教学大纲规定的教学时数要求；“教材版本”一项，必须写清：出版社、出版日期、版次、编者等。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:36px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">、最后两周为考试周，不包含在教学周数内。</span></p><p><br/></p>',NULL,'2018-04-24','2018-04-24');

