ding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:   宋体\">女</span></p></td><td width=\"29\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">53</span></p></td><td width=\"47\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:   宋体\">硕士</span></p></td><td width=\"47\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:   宋体\">教授</span></p></td><td width=\"198\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">1 &nbsp; Research on Hierarchical Interactive Teaching Model Based on Naive Bayesian &nbsp; Classification</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，《</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Advances &nbsp; in Computer Science Research</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">, &nbsp; 2018.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">volume &nbsp; 80</span></p><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倾斜车牌图像边缘模糊特征识别方法研究，《计算机仿真》</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">,2017.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基于</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">EEMD</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">结合二次小包降噪胡齿轮箱故障诊断，《中北大学学报（自然科学版）》，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2015.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p></td><td width=\"236\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公共场所智能垃圾桶系统的设计，《山西电子技术》，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2017.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">超材料研究及应用探讨，</span><span style=\"font-family:   &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2017.11.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，办公自动化。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电工电子技术实训课程教学改革探索与实践，《办公自动化》，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2016.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家用水域定时自动增氧喂料控制器的改进设计，《山西电子技术》，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2016.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p></td><td width=\"175\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:29px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">快速分选富集循环肿瘤癌细胞的过滤式微流控芯片的研究，科技厅面上青年基金项目，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2017.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:29px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">应用技术型人才培养课程体系改革，横向委托项目，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2017.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:29px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">山西大学商务学院</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">达内大数据开发校外实践基地建设，横向委托项目，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2017.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:29px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电子信息类专业大学生实践创新能力培养的实践研究，山西省教育科学“十三五”规划课题，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2016.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:29px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">碎片化学习时代翻转课堂实验教学模式构建研究，山西省教育科学“十二五”规划课题，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2016.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:29px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电子技术类技能竞赛与实践教学融通的实践研究，山西省教育科学“十二五”规划课题，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2016.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:29px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基于</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">DOM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Web</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">信息抽取技术研究，学院科研项目，</span><span style=\"font-family:   &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2016.10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"63\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:   宋体\">董妍汝</span></p></td><td width=\"39\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:   宋体\">女</span></p></td><td width=\"29\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">37</span></p></td><td width=\"47\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:   宋体\">硕士</span></p></td><td width=\"47\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:   宋体\">副教授</span></p></td><td width=\"198\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><br/></td><td width=\"236\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基于最短路径的旅游咨询网站的设计与应用，《山西电子技术》，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2017.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电子信息科学与技术专业实践教学体系研究，《山西电子技术》，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2015.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p></td><td width=\"175\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电子技术类技能竞赛与实践教学融通的实践研究，山西省教育科学“十三五”规划课题，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2015.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">微博舆情话题识别与追踪方法研究及平台构建，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\"> 2016</span><span style=\"font-family:   宋体\">山西省重点研发计划</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">社会发展方向，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2016.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:31px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基于应用型人才培养的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">O2O</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">教学模式研究</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">山西省教育科学“十